 experiences\", \"from\": 188, \"to\": 203}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic games\", \"from\": 207, \"to\": 224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde, who was 19 at the time of theoffencewith a 12-year-old girl, cried as he said he had considered not taking part.\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 353, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van de Velde\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 239}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 255, \"to\": 263}, {\"ngram\": \"a 12-year-old girl\", \"from\": 282, \"to\": 300}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The publication of a photograph of his wife by a British tabloid \\\"almost broke me\\\", he told reporters.\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 403, \"end\": 410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9948682292415439, \"rank\": 0.004738796335497443, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The publication\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 369}, {\"ngram\": \"a photograph\", \"from\": 373, \"to\": 385}, {\"ngram\": \"his wife\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 397}, {\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did something wrong 10 years ago and I have to live with that,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 533, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 474}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But hurting people close to me, whether Matthew Immers (his volleyball partner), my wife, my child\\u2026 that is going too far.\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 657, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 547, \"to\": 553}, {\"ngram\": \"Matthew Immers\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 589}, {\"ngram\": \"his volleyball partner\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 613}, {\"ngram\": \"my wife\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 623}, {\"ngram\": \"my child\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There wasindeeda moment when I thought 'isit worth it?'.\\\"\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 715, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"There wasindeeda moment\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 681}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Throughout the Olympics Van der Velde was followed by the world's media and booed whenever on court since it emerged that in 2016 he had beenconvicted of child rape in Englandand had served over a year in jail for the crime.\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 941, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics Van der\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"Velde\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 754}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's media\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 788}, {\"ngram\": \"court\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 816}, {\"ngram\": \"child rape\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 881}, {\"ngram\": \"Englandand\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 895}, {\"ngram\": \"over a year\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 918}, {\"ngram\": \"jail\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 926}, {\"ngram\": \"the crime\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 940}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Theoffencetook place when he was 19 and his victim was 12, which automatically qualifies as rape in English law.\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Theoffencetook place\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 962}, {\"ngram\": \"his victim\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 992}, {\"ngram\": \"rape\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1038}, {\"ngram\": \"English law\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1053}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite widespread calls for him to be banned, the InternationalOlympicsCommittee said it could not stop the Netherlands from sending an athlete who qualified in the usual way.\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1232, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1165, \"end\": 1176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9995402032533924, \"rank\": 0.0004536891130197078, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/r